<p>Sending large files across the Internet isn&#8217;t always easy, and Dave and John go through some options for doing this today. Then it&#8217;s straight to the mailbag, sharing some great tips sent in by listeners, including an awesome app for creating audio comments.</p>
<p><strong>Show notes for TMO To Go: Mac Geek Gab For September 3rd, 2005</strong></p>
<p>Podcast Link: <a href="http://mp3.macobserver.com/podcast/mgg14.mp3" data-wpel-link="external" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer">TMO To Go: Mac Geek Gab, September 3rd, 2005</a></p>
<p>Sending large files across the Internet isn&#8217;t always easy, and Dave and John go through some options for doing this today. Then it&#8217;s straight to the mailbag, sharing some great tips sent in by listeners, including an awesome app for creating audio comments.</p>
